And aiming at schism they do the observanceday procedure by reciting the Monastic Code
When theyve just finished and none of the gathering has left an equal number of resident monks arrive
In such a case what has been recited is valid and the late arrivals should announce their purity in the presence of the others
And theres a serious offense for the reciters
