When a procedure of ejection for not giving up a bad view has another three qualities it is also illegitimate contrary to the Monastic Law and not properly resolved it is done without having charged the person with their offense it is done illegitimately it is done by an incomplete assembly
The group of twelve on illegitimate legal procedures of ejection for not giving up a bad view is finished
The group of twelve on legitimate legal procedures
